    isReversed
    title="Mallemo is your guide in the remodeling of your home"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Improves functionality',
        description:
          'You can reorganize spaces to better suit your current needs.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Increases property value',
        description:
          'Remodeling can increase your homes value, which can be beneficial if you decide to sell it in the future.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Improves safety',
        description:
          'You can update outdated electrical and plumbing systems, reducing the risk of accidents.',
